        <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin: 10px 0;">6:00 AM - 12:00 AM</p>
        <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.8;">Happy Hour: 3 PM - 5 PM</p>
